---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Paradigm IT Services."
>
  <main class="bg-surface min-h-screen">
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-on-surface">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 font-body text-on-surface/80 leading-relaxed">
          <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly, including name, email address, and message content when you contact us via our contact form or subscribe to our newsletter. We do not collect payment information — all billing is handled through separate secure channels.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to respond to inquiries, deliver newsletter communications you have opted into, and improve our services. We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain contact form submissions for up to 24 months and newsletter subscriptions until you unsubscribe. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Cookies</h2>
          <p>Our website uses minimal cookies — primarily for analytics. We use anonymized, aggregate analytics data only. No personal data is stored in cookies.</p>
          
          <h2 class="font-sans text-xl text-on-surface font-medium mt-8">Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@serviceparadigm.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@serviceparadigm.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
